n仔咪一樣會話無feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a669ec3ecae53d88c65c919b9bdb2fdf41412d","tid":392875,"uid":130342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:15:35.000Z","msg":"回不去了"},{"pid":"4925bb311f1f9961ed0865523409bb22f4233fac","tid":392875,"uid":65870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問題是當繼續落去, 對雙方都會係傷受時, 分手是最好的選擇...<br />\n這是最無奈, 卻是最實際的做法....<br />\n<br />\n當然, 決定前要諗清楚, 亦要努力過....</blockquote><br />\n受傷少不免，唯有靠自己改變想法，你唔踏出呢一步去維繫，亦唔好期待對方，施比受更有福<br />\n你正面對待，我相信終究會令大家好"},{"pid":"8ee771a1cefbc768744969704aaf09b58b82a42e","tid":392875,"uid":65870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T07:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後都係分開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得要搵個你又中意佢佢又中意你既人其實好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係難，所以先要珍惜<br />\n希望你遇到下一個能夠避免再一次嘅分離"},{"pid":"6ace636004427961efa44a21ec833d7cc5c3a5cb","tid":392875,"uid":67398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:18:55.000Z","msg":"樓主我愛你"}]}